                                <h4 class="detail-section-title">Summary</h4>
                                <p class="detail-description">A comprehensive guide to navigating and using the ThinkBridge ERP system
                                    effectively.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="detail-section">
                                    <h4 class="detail-section-title">Content</h4>
                                    <div class="article-content-preview">
                                        <p>Welcome to ThinkBridge ERP! This guide will help you get started with the system and understand
                                            its core features.</p>
                                            <h5>1. Dashboard Overview</h5>
                                            <p>The dashboard provides a quick overview of your projects, tasks, and team activity. You can
                                                customize widgets to show the information most relevant to you.</p>
                                                <h5>2. Navigation</h5>
                                                <p>Use the sidebar to navigate between different modules. The main sections include Projects, Tasks,
                                                    Team, Documents, and Reports.</p>
                                                    <h5>3. Getting Help</h5>
                                                    <p>If you need assistance, check the Knowledge Base or contact your system administrator.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

